
1. downlaod and install MongoDB from www.mongodb.com
2. create data->db and log folder insite mongodb installed folder
3. navigate from admin cmd into bin folder
4. set mongodb flag by running: mongod --directoryperdb --dbpath C:\mongodb\db --logpath C:\mongodb\log\mongo.log --logappend --rest --install
5. start mongodb service by running: net start mongoDB
6. access mongodb shell navigate from cmd into bin folder and run mongo

Mongo DB functionalities: mongo --username alice --password abc123 --host mongodb0.tutorials.com --port 28015
show dbs
use db_name

